      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">16.207-3</ph> Limitations.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">This contract type may be used only when-</p>
         <ol id="d982e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1004e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The
work required cannot otherwise be clearly defined;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1004e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The required
